Doom 3 GPL Source Code
dhewm3 Vulkan - Temporal EMA resolve compute shader for AO.

Blends the current frame's raw AO image into a per-slot history image using
an exponential moving average:
    history = mix(history, current, alpha)

When alpha == 1.0 (first frame or camera cut), history is replaced directly
with current to avoid reads from uninitialized or stale history.

